# Support Vector Machine (SVM) on MNIST Dataset

This project implements Support Vector Machines (SVM) to classify handwritten digits from the MNIST dataset. The performance is evaluated using two SVM kernels: **Linear** and **Radial Basis Function (RBF)**.

---

## **Table of Contents**
1. [Overview](#overview)
